 1917 Sunday 28 Jan . Last night pass without a call We did not get up till 9a.m . Noth do , but to get breakfast sit in dugout all day . Got 2 carri today one for each squad . Our came on after dark just befor tea . Exhaustion case . Machin gun fire make us duck onc or twice . Get back safe . Sever shell lob on top of dugout but no damag . Ridg I go for water . Write home letter No. 28 one to Mrs. Grant .
